{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My-- I must say, that in-- my brothers, none of them looked Jewish or the sisters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we-- they didn't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They risked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because, for menswear-- for menswear, what we had in Dzialoszyce, for one suit, you could get a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they used to go outside the city and bring chickens or bread or anything, milk, everything for that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we had-- really, we didn't suffer with the hunger at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they traded the clothes--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we traded, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--lots of Poles, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That they were happy to do it, because you couldn't find during-- after the-- the war a suit or something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had beautiful things, because, from the shop, we took everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we really didn't know-- didn't know what hunger means, because we had plenty to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm sure lots of people suffered a terrible lot, because there was no food around in the city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, as the time was getting on, it was getting so bad that it was just impossible to live anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were killing people and taking people to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we heard that people were taken to Belzec or things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found out that they were gassed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, people were worrying, really, that, you know, what will happen to us?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When did you find that out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What year was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was in '42, already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '42, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The year after that, we left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, when-- a few days before, we heard that the Germans are coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're going to liquidate the whole city, and all the Jews will go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no one knew what will happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we heard this, we were trying to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
